data.description: Bright and spacious, this Silver Springs cutie feels like a brand new home! With its large living room and bedrooms filled with natural light, it's a trendy haven. The updated kitchen and laundry room offer plenty of stylish cabinets, while the kitchen boasts amazing counter space and sleek stainless steel appliances. You'll love the skylight too! This home is ready for your personal touch, with ceiling fans in every room and pressure-treated decks. Get ready to make it your own on this fantastic-sized lot!
